with rulers?

01:14.500 --> 01:16.400
That's not allowed anymore.

01:16.700 --> 01:18.900
We do need those
burial records, Father.

01:19.000 --> 01:21.300
And since this is a federally
protected historic site--

01:21.400 --> 01:22.800
Fine.
But I'll

01:22.900 --> 01:24.800
to show some respect
for where you are.

01:24.900 --> 01:26.400
This is
consecrated ground.

01:26.500 --> 01:28.300
When did you say the last person
was buried here?

01:28.400 --> 01:29.800
1951.

01:29.900 --> 01:31.000
This is a male,

01:31.100 --> 01:33.900
buried no more than five
years ago without a casket.

01:34.000 --> 01:35.000
That's impossible.

01:35.100 --> 01:37.300
There's evidence of trauma
to the frontal bone.

01:37.400 --> 01:38.800
Looks like a fatal assault.

01:38.900 --> 01:40.300
Arrange for a
forensic team.

01:40.400 --> 01:41.900
Hodgins will want
to collect soil

01:42.000 --> 01:43.700
for bugs and particulates.
I'll call Booth.

01:44.300 --> 01:46.400
I'm afraid your ground
was consecrated

01:46.400 --> 01:48.400
as a crime scene, Father.

01:51.500 --> 01:53.700
You know, the priest
made a complaint.pl

01:53.900 --> 01:55.600
He said that you made fun

01:55.700 --> 01:57.700
