No, I didn't.

01:57.800 --> 01:59.700
Perhaps I was
a bit colorful.
Colorful?

01:59.900 --> 02:00.800
Writerly.

02:00.900 --> 02:02.300
I am a best-selling author,
Booth.

02:02.400 --> 02:04.100
Victim is 30 to 40 years old.

02:04.200 --> 02:05.700
He's an old school priest,
Bones.

02:05.800 --> 02:07.300
So I'm supposed to walk
on eggshells

02:07.400 --> 02:09.199
because someone believes
that a plot  earth

