arithmetic supposed to stand?

18:04.300 --> 18:07.200
So your problem with Dr.
Brennan is that you don't know

18:07.300 --> 18:10.700
what will or will not catch
fire or where you stand.

18:13.700 --> 18:15.200
What?
That's good.

18:15.800 --> 18:18.300
You know, that's,
that's very good.

18:23.800 --> 18:27.000
The CDC shows that you
contracted coccidioidomycosis

18:27.100 --> 18:28.200
three years ago.

18:28.500 --> 18:30.000
The only case
in the area.

18:30.500 --> 18:33.100
Well, you know, I,
I, I used to do a lot

18:33.200 --> 18:34.700
of odd jobs
around the parish.

18:35.400 --> 18:36.900
I'd help Father
Donlan in the garden.

18:37.000 --> 18:38.500
I'm sure that's how
I contracted it.

18:38.600 --> 18:40.700
Nice try, Enzo,
but your name also came up

18:40.800 --> 18:43.000
