away with if you hadn't hit

18:45.900 --> 18:46.800
the water main.

18:48.600 --> 18:49.600
I want a lawyer.

18:49.700 --> 18:50.600
Yeah, nice way to get him

18:50.700 --> 18:51.400
to clam up,
thanks.

18:54.100 --> 18:55.500
So why'd you kill
Father McCourt?

18:55.600 --> 18:57.100
Did he catch you?
