19:12.000 --> 19:13.300
Jewelry just buried.

19:13.400 --> 19:14.100
You know.

19:16.100 --> 19:17.500
I figured no one
would miss it.

19:19.200 --> 19:21.300
I didn't kill anybody, okay?

19:22.500 --> 19:24.800
Father McCourt and me, we
