You said
that we would talk.

20:49.900 --> 20:50.900
Yeah, well,
guess what?

20:51.000 --> 20:51.400
Hmm?

20:52.100 --> 20:53.300
I got distracted.

21:05.100 --> 21:07.000
I can't believe
Father McCourt's dead.

21:09.100 --> 21:11.300
I mean, I, I thought
he just took off.

21:12.000 --> 21:13.400
You two were pretty close.

21:13.700 --> 21:14.400
Yeah.

21:15.200 --> 21:16.700
I w-- I was an altar boy.

21:16.800 --> 21:17.800
Yeah, so was I.

21:18.500 --> 21:21.200
I liked our priest,
