23:29.500 --> 23:31.900
quite a few priests
have come and gone

23:32.000 --> 23:32.900
during your tenure.

23:33.600 --> 23:36.300
Given who they send me,
I've done well.

23:36.600 --> 23:37.800
Who do they send you?

23:37.900 --> 23:40.700
Priests who need firm guidance,
for the most part.

