In 1997, a complaint was sworn
against you for assault.

23:44.500 --> 23:48.400
Is that your idea
of "firm guidance"?

23:48.500 --> 23:50.600
It was not assault,
it was corporal punishment.

23:50.700 --> 23:52.900
I found an altar boy
drinking sacramental wine

23:53.000 --> 23:54.500
from the chalice.
